    Enum for different separation technologies used as a preprocessing step before the actual data point acquisition.

    A separation type will usually provide additional information for acquired MsScan objects. The most common case being a chromatographic separation coupled to a mass spectrometer. Here, the chromatograph would provide the retention time of each acquired data point as additional information.
